      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SOUL PANORAMIC (1) was below best at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth at Richmond, but was among the placings at Wentworth Park three back. Look for sharp improvement here. SILVER REIN (4) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing seventh (23.31) last time in a Mix 3/4 at Maitland. Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Should be about the mark. MAJOR SOKO (7) racing well without winning, placing at her last four runs. Last start finished 2nd on February 25 over 320m at Richmond behind Jennifer Juniper beaten 4 lengths (18.60) in a Mix 2/3. Can measure up. TILLY THE FILLY (8) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.",
